Isaiah 21-7 <t>When he sees riders, horsemen in pairs, </t><t>riders on donkeys, riders on camels, </t><t>let him listen diligently, </t><t>very diligently.”</t>
Isaiah 21-8 <t>Then he who saw cried out: <f>[2]</f> </t><t><f>ⓛ</f>“Upon a watchtower I stand, O Lord, </t><t>continually by day, </t><t>and at my post I am stationed </t><t>whole nights.</t>
