Isaiah 21-15 <t>For they have fled from the swords, </t><t>from the drawn sword, </t><t>from the bent bow, </t><t>and from the press of battle. </t>
Isaiah 21-16 <pb/>For thus the Lord said to me, “Within a year, <f>ⓑ</f>according to the years of a hired worker, all the glory of <f>ⓒ</f>Kedar will come to an end.
